    "body": "As discussed, this is now seen as an optimisation rather than a fix, because in the case of invalid block, the internal variable `trieDbState` of Blockchain is reset to `nil` and on the next `insertChain` invocation, the state gets reloaded from the database. It used to break due to other bug, which is now fixed: https://github.com/ledgerwatch/turbo-geth/issues/118",
